content:
Use managed packages to distribute CRM Analytics.

Keep in mind the following considerations when using packages:

* Use managed packages, not unmanaged.
* Deploy from namespaced orgs to namespaced orgs.
* Avoid manually packaging individual datasets, dataflows, and assets.
* Don't remove assets from packages, as this can cause deployment errors.
* Understand dataset and dataflow dependencies in packages.
* Datasets from managed packages can't be used in dashboards as a connected data source.
* Saved dashboard views aren't included in packages.

See also:

* Salesforce DX Developer Guide: Second-Generation Managed Packages
* Use the Metadata API for CRM Analytics Assets and User XMD
title: CRM Analytics Packaging Considerations
